	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By spoole</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Nov  2, 2005, 15:12</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=Smedley%27s%20Mistake&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2FOpEd%2Farticle_37.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
